{"title":"海上人（外一首）","authors":["马砚田"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":3,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上人（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马砚田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收海的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是海上人感情最富足的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子和儿女笑着跑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海风清朗着太阳极富诗意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不收海的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是海上人感觉最萧条的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但岁月揉拌霜雪晨昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在烟锅里翩翩起舞的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧是永恒的渔歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想结识海吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就读一读海上人的表情吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海每天和他们耳语　男子汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做丈夫和父亲的秘密"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排浪不对胃口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海风老觊觎你的舌头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明灭的渔火爱唠叨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是不肯把心思掏出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人也一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离开城市　便"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不见涂着唇膏粉黛的广告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塑料和别的什么制成的苍白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气球般急剧膨胀的念头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"体味海滩月色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把脑子里那团什么全扔到海里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在孤独中孤独"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟是味道不错的享受"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}